API URL: https://developer.github.com/v3/repos/

list of all repos for an org
==================================
>>  https://api.github.com/orgs/OODD-Mozilla/repos

list of all pull requests
=============================
>> https://api.github.com/repos/OODD-Mozilla/TestRepo/pulls?state=all

git commits for the pull request
==================================
GET /repos/:owner/:repo/pulls/:number/commits

>> https://api.github.com/repos/OODD-Mozilla/TestRepo/pulls/1/commits

